{"tid":2504983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《蘋果》「假新聞」稱奧斯卡男配角聲援香港　連登仔查證「隻字未提Hong Kong」","createTime":"2021-04-26T09:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T10:37:14.000Z","uid":283837,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d982438790336bf1c7430a0bea25758a96d8808","tid":2504983,"uid":283837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"【橙訊】《第93屆奧斯卡頒獎禮》今日（26日）舉行，男星Daniel Kaluuya以黑人抗爭電影《Judas and the Black Messiah》奪得最佳男配角。《蘋果日報》報道時指Daniel Kaluuya在領獎時，提出「香港抗爭者」展現了團結的力量。經一眾網民查證後，發現得獎感言隻字未提「Hong Kong」。<br />\n<br />\n「連登討論區」網民翻查得獎影片後發現，Daniel Kaluuya僅在台上多次致謝，當中致謝詞時原句為「when they play divide and conquer」，意指黑豹黨，被《蘋果日報》誤解成聲援「香港抗爭者」並以「男配角得主撐香港抗爭」為題報道。<br />\n<br />\n網民證實全文並未提及香港相關言論，直斥報道「炒車」。《蘋果日報》其後發出道歉聲明，承認報道失實。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.orangenews.hk/details?recommendId=1111208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.orangenews.hk%2Fdetails%3FrecommendId%3D1111208&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=caf085d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.orangenews.hk/details?recommendId=1111208</a>"},{"pid":"295bec5f8d78c6c93021e59edb2e83cd06ef4bd0","tid":2504983,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:32:01.000Z","msg":"連登仔出賣蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1546e1b50a0b50293d62a6f1181de86069732ee6","tid":2504983,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"紅煤 拉"},{"pid":"301517bc2cbf34af4791bf8f70080665ccbe3b7b","tid":2504983,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:12:20.000Z","msg":"人哋蘋果至少有道歉 你地日日炒 潛水當冇事 而家一日唔偷雞就做保長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbd3d300960d2936363bae3a80c63e5a43f5dfd","tid":2504983,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:37:14.000Z","msg":"橙新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}